The paper discusses research collaboration and the novelty of the resulting work. Based on this, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), as it deals with social dynamics and collaboration. Other likely categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
